{"tid":796202,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"主婦手點搞","createTime":"2018-08-27T15:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:52:18.000Z","uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4057cc115b4dabb2530efd5465da0b1356bed5fb","tid":796202,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"我媽睇醫生開D藥膏搽左又無用, 一唔搽又返發,<br />\n搽個隻澳洲潤膚康同凡士林搽又無用,<br />\n買左隻施巴洗手夜比佢洗手又無用,<br />\n已經平時戴手套做野,<br />\n都係又痕又爆血,<br />\n有咩方法可以好返?"},{"pid":"af58b25e817a6efe4d3313125657d2acf0ec18bb","tid":796202,"uid":201731,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"有冇師奶腳"},{"pid":"5cc9cdd6476a92f831fa34700587e43f8106ee91","tid":796202,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"搽埋右啦"},{"pid":"500a539dc2a8993cb5ca06baf11c74f9748e4dfb","tid":796202,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"我都試過啊 pt返侍應搞到主婦手<br />\n個陣係r到中指指紋就嚟冇咁滯<br />\n後尾狂search 搵到支skin relief cream<br />\n搽咗好似兩三個月 就冇事喇<br />\n不過到而家已經過咗四五年<br />\n我唔知間嘢仲有冇賣<br />\n我個陣係喺間叫c竇嘅鋪到買 尖沙咀山林道<br />\n而家唔知有冇搬到<br />\n支野個樣好似條link咁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.theztyle.com/home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=541&amp;do=blog&amp;id=202894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theztyle.com%2Fhome.php%3Fmod%3Dspace%26uid%3D541%26do%3Dblog%26id%3D202894&d=W4EWNGLU8kWabEt6zhMsOUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e3d54075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.theztyle.com/home.php?mod=space&amp;uid=541&amp;do=blog&amp;id=202894</a>"},{"pid":"455cfd07425874f0ac8a9e69608ec4a7b7aa673b","tid":796202,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:36:34.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"10040ebcf0d71eb959586bcb576d662f201981ea","tid":796202,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T20:57:28.000Z","msg":"主婦手係長期接觸清漯劑、熱水，又唔搽手霜引致<br />\n<br />\n以後無論天氣乾唔乾燥，都要